<h1>Documentation</h1>
<p class="lede">Step-by-step guides for using FISCO, with linked video tutorials.</p>

<h2>Workflow</h2>

<article class="card">
  <h3>Step 1 — Set global parameters</h3>
  <p>Country selection, base year, plan horizon, and country-specific overrides.</p>
  <p><a href="https://youtu.be/xFtRbp9mPsE" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Watch tutorial &rarr;</a></p>
</article>

<article class="card" style="margin-top: 1rem">
  <h3>Step 2 — Update outturn data</h3>
  <p>One-click Eurostat fetch via the <code>EurostatUpdateVBA</code> (Windows) or <code>EurostatUpdateMac</code> macros. AMECO series are entered manually.</p>
  <p><a href="https://youtu.be/PTS-xMeD0Sw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Watch tutorial &rarr;</a></p>
</article>

<article class="card" style="margin-top: 1rem">
  <h3>Step 3 — Enter plan</h3>
  <p>Recommended net-expenditure path, discretionary revenue measures, and one-off measures. Optionally load the defence-clause scenario.</p>
  <p><a href="https://youtu.be/30qsKPsrdjA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Watch tutorial &rarr;</a></p>
</article>

